title: [TYPE]  #4387 is a APE/HUMAN
body:
BGAN V2 TRAIT CONSTITUTION

 ACCORDING TO FINALIZED TRAIT CONSTITUTION BASTARD #4387 SHOULD BE CLASSIFIED AS:

APE/HUMAN CLASSIFICATION
1.1.9 

1. Combination of ape and large specific characteristics, with a focus on nose and face outline.
2. Ape nostrils with no ape face outline.
3. Ape face outline and regular double or single pixel nostril.

Note: THE DARK NECK AND LIGHT FACE WASN'T AN OFFICIAL APE CLASSIFICATION UNTIL RECENTLY. 

(1.1.3 Ape) clear distinction between color on side of the ape face and front of the ape face
